Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們已經遲了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父王一定等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海恩絲，快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們還未找到迪拉姆的行蹤？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀打敗了藍迪斯王之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟住隨即把王位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓了給遊牧民族長迪歐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之後就一個人四處流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這件事倒底是怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藍迪斯王家族行動受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而蒂雅娜又行蹤未明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我兒子究竟是不是和蒂雅娜一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在一起的機會很大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們這班正飯桶！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這段時間你們到底查到些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是我們家族最英勇的青年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要我們能運用你精湛的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去壓制多利亞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將會為我們國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶來無限的繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在正進行一個大計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對不能有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父王，我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬倫，我等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次我去跟沙士的商人交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經談好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎？那辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在還不能用武力來對付多利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暫時只能用經濟手段來拉攏他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，一切聽從父王吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有，快找出迪拉姆的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，我馬倫一定會完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Presented by 啄木鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這兒就是沙士了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧為貿易都市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若當初不是征服了多利亞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信也不會像現在那麼繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀主人，我們快點入城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道啦，別那麼心急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王一定很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他知道我那麼自由一定會很妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞市真繁榮呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最重要的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論什麼店舖也是生意滔滔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那的確是迪歐國王來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈娜，不能讓馬倫王子失望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們只許成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道啦，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得肚子餓，去吃東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是多利亞的衛兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的辛苦他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別忘記你是國王來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那沒辦法，他們好像已知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一定是伊米魯的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是你領導有方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞才回復十多年前那樣繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許我們應該多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一個曾經幫忙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若沒有亞秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結果可能不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王，請恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞現在那麼繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會遭不少國家妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們週圍有很多國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都想侵佔我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其是北方的咕普達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直都虎視眈眈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我希望國王你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯，你又這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的聽厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，迪歐國王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這樣微服出巡很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們根本不知敵人會何時偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是做國王真的太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶然出來散散心也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是人之常情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望你能瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我點自由好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你真的要特別小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真令人傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但做人就太過緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯是關心你的安全才會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯是個人才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論學識和其它方面都很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我認為他是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞不能缺少的楝樑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的那麼優秀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這都是國王你一向讚他的說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣吧，菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由明天開始，妳去服待伊米魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這主意也不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烏路絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在考慮明日把妳封為新王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事？不喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，跟我現在的身份…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹嘛？妳不想當王妃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對我來說，我情願像現在那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨著國王你四處去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳說得真對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老闆，麻煩你給我三份燒肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有，加壺特級馬倫拿酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命呀，來人呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王，國王，你要忍著呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弊傢伙，那匕首有毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,匕首有毒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王你不能有事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些是什麼水果來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看看那頸鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很奪目，很漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，別離我太遠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳才是最貴重的商品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要稍一不慎，妳就會被人搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還會被人高價賣上船去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若妳真的被人買了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就算出多多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都未必能把妳買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀，我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這花花世界什麼人都有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且壞人特別多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，我們先去吃點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厲害，不愧是謝瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算我跟他來也會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已經想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如就此認輸算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我這局棋還未輸定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對，還有機會贏的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等，你走這步就必輸無疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死丫頭，誰叫你來多管閒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的奴隸太多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在代她向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是我太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我身為下人，竟然那麼口多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，請原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行，絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟這商人的賭局剛要決定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳在此搗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說一句對不起就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你要我怎樣才行算數
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莫非你要在此當眾懲罰她？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用，你只是她的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想難為你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說到尾，我謝瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是沙士有名的商人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看妳的樣子，也像個會下棋的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才妳不是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這局棋還有勝出機會的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那妳一定有把屋贏我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小女子不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才，妳真的有這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都聽到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呀，我也聽到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如妳來代他繼續下這一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有異議嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，你剛才的賭注我還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的賭注
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就改用這丫頭的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什麼出奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若妳勝出的話我這個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亦都將會屬於妳的主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但若妳輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那妳就屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳主人就不能帶妳走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧，謝瑞加先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你既然喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你就和蒂雅娜來下這一局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣？蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若主人你允許的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就奉陪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，丫頭，妳坐那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失禮了，我就大膽的來跟大爺來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就從剛才最後一步開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來這局棋還有這一著的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下來輪到大爺你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道，不用妳來提我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她這一步是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一步很出名的棋步來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她只是個奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但竟然會使出這一著棋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她這一著，好絕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一著是多利亞人迪安德…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...的「八善棋式」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼吵，叫我怎下棋呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大爺，你想清楚了沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的決定這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，我決定這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我三步之內就會贏你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒可能，怎可能會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的棋藝真的很精湛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實精湛的是妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想問問，妳怎會那麼棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可否告訴我從那兒學來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾經跟迪安德先生學過幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪不得，我一見到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就已經覺得妳與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閣下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫亞秀，叫我亞秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀，你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你擁有一位最優秀的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要好好的珍惜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你的讚賞，我一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然大家那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如大家齊齊喝杯酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這棋局我輸了，你帶她走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫做希耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉，妳不是我的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勝出的是蒂雅娜，她是屬於妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要我要我就要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連奴隸都有奴隸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的聞所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是她們兩個都是女人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次真的有排搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事呀，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳不要叫我主人，叫我蒂雅娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳跟謝瑞加很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是兩天前把我從市集買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳只是跟了他兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那他對你怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有好好的對待妳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝瑞加先生很不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我不懂得怎樣去取悅主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以謝瑞加先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才會把我送給人家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都怪我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到會把妳搞成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…這根本與主人妳無關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不是主人，是蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經是妳的奴隸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，我來教妳怎樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，你到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你在旁邊好好欣賞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在主人面前是沒有任何秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把衣服脫下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳的身材真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且樣貌亦很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉，來取悅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，蒂雅娜主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請妳來享用希耶拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好可愛呀，希耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜主人呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣了？希耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是很想亞秀主人來享用妳？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本就沒有這樣想過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳不用忍得那麼辛苦的，說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳很想是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀主人，你聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你來享用希耶拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,記得謝瑞加先生怎樣說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若然我勝出的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就會把希耶拉送給主人你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯，他曾經這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，這樣我感到很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是算了吧，蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道我沒有什麼魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以不會有人喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這全都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉，根本不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過，謝瑞加主人就是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才會把我送給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉，妳很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若然這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就請亞秀主人來享用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行呀，這兒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀主人，你好勁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實我當初見到你和柏麗斯時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想在你享用她時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也一起來享用我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？為何妳會改變主意呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧，亞秀主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想把希耶拉買回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯，你知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是謝瑞加是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沙士其中的一個大富商
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它的也不用多講了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一句到尾，我出五十個金幣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用五十個金幣買回她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝瑞加主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看不出你那麼重視希耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對，你說得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉，妳認為怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不想回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以的話，我願意跟他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就讓希耶拉跟你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了，你留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，妳認為怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就照主人意思去辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的太好了，希耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來謝瑞加先生很重視妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝瑞加主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我太過注重於勝負這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然把妳當賭注來下注
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的太糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請妳原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事實上，我覺得是我不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本與主人你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天晚上，多得兩位主人教導
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才真正明白到快樂的真諦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼，妳是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我比起以前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更加喜歡晚上一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做那一種翻雲覆雨的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來希耶拉真的那麼厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我來請求主人你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,處罰我這個淫亂的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來妳已經學會了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那今晚我就來領教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看妳有何進步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你們兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在此衷心向你們致謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了，妳的棋藝那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可否告訴我是從那兒學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我在多利亞皇宮做奴隸時學的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在多利亞皇宮學的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了，多利亞的王族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽說他們國王在市集被暗器行刺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們有聽說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？迪歐國王…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被人行刺？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好極了，亞爾貝爾多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遲點我一定會打賞你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我目的根本不是要殿下你的賞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想向你表示我的忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多謝你對我一片忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以向你保証
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你對我的忠心一定不會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多謝殿下你對我的保証
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,屬下先行告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬倫殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海恩絲，什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的會重用這個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一種人對我一定有存在價值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要相信我用人的技巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很對不起，馬倫殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我竟然對你的才能有懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我雖然一直都在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但竟然沒法保護他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是若當時不是妳在他身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把血吸了出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信他早已一命嗚呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，我只是盡自己能力罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,御醫怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信迪歐國王會平安無事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,關於迪拉姆的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們已經在追查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:22:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但還是一點消息也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之一有消息就立即通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有第二句話能說的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顧問官每次問你這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都是這樣推我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為我最近沒時間到皇宮去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以真的一點消息也收不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但聽說迪拉姆殿下戰後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經和一美女同遊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，沒留一點痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和美女一起同遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太失禮人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即是說我們的迪拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身為王子都出來胡混！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但消息傳來是這樣報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟你說也是浪費氣力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有誰能答到我這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去找他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暫時無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自從藍迪斯王自殺之後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就連蒂雅娜也失去蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知的只有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那迪歐國王也應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽說他們攻佔皇宮時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王都是其中一名猛將
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我見見他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但這個時候不太方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顧問官，請你說清楚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事實上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王在微服出巡時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遇到刺客行刺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以現在不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這件事，我現在才知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.85,0:24:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那國王他怎樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.37,0:24:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還幸運，暫時沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.41,0:24:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那真的很好運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但有件事很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.33,0:24:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些沙士商人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已決定要到此來開評議會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.85,0:24:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一次會議也很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.85,0:24:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這班沙士商人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.21,0:24:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你們的國家代表
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.89,0:24:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要商討明年的貿易
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知這班沙士商人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想和國王親自會面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們明天就會抵達貴國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.89,0:24:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果國王不接見他們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.89,0:24:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,襲擊迪歐國王的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.05,0:24:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了，應是咕普達的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.01,0:25:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠迪歐國王的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞才可以在短短幾個月內
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.49,0:25:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恢復週圍各國的邦交
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.81,0:25:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都要有你幫忙才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.49,0:25:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千萬別這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.01,0:25:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我除了文學之外
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.13,0:25:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它事情都一竅不通
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.89,0:25:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王他為了這國家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以和沙士商人通商
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.13,0:25:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就下令批準…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.81,0:25:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遊牧民族來多利亞經商
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.85,0:25:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,令這兒開創了貿易網
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.93,0:25:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的很全心全意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.85,0:25:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對，不論多貴重的物品也好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.41,0:25:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能在這兒買得到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.89,0:25:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就已經有足夠吸引力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.97,0:25:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有，若這國家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.81,0:25:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有利的消息傳出
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.89,0:25:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那又怎會繁榮呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.21,0:25:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說得不錯，全對
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.21,0:25:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一般這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要用幾年時間才能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.89,0:25:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是國王他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.01,0:25:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是用了幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.81,0:25:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不單止得到沙士商人的讚賞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.21,0:25:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是得到了遊牧民族的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.49,0:25:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到我們國家來通商
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.81,0:26:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們的辦事能力真的很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.93,0:26:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之就是難得一見
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.01,0:26:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是個超級王者來的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.85,0:26:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在在多利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.77,0:26:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒甚麼是買不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.97,0:26:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以各國商人都爭相到此
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.85,0:26:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因為這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.13,0:26:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以他就受到咕普達的襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.89,0:26:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀殿下，你有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.45,0:26:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有話不怕跟我說，亞秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莫非你不相信我？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.97,0:26:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是我不相信你，伊米魯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.53,0:26:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你應知道你是多利亞的顧問官
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.25,0:26:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你如果要保護主人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.53,0:26:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就需要，這個
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.13,0:26:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.93,0:26:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道就行了，別說出去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.85,0:26:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你身上有了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.29,0:26:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那即是代表你的身份就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.37,0:26:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王他，曾經和我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有我的父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.21,0:26:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起滴血為盟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.89,0:26:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們曾經滴血為盟？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.89,0:26:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那即是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.53,0:26:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有如親兄弟一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.97,0:26:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真多謝你，亞秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.97,0:26:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在我心中的疑團
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.89,0:27:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經全都解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.57,0:27:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次危難，要全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.93,0:27:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在正面臨的問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.85,0:27:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.89,0:27:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了，我會作好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.85,0:27:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那拜託你了，但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.41,0:27:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有一件事令我很煩惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.85,0:27:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咕普達的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.97,0:27:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正在不斷追查迪拉姆王子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.89,0:27:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又不能找人來頂罪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.05,0:27:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果再這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.25,0:27:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們一定能找到藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.89,0:27:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.21,0:27:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次大件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.25,0:28:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.85,0:28:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我，殺迪拉姆的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要我去認罪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.29,0:28:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就萬事皆休了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.33,0:28:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.77,0:28:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,令妳成為奴隸的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.37,0:28:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和妳無關
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.25,0:28:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.05,0:28:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，若果不是因為我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.41,0:28:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.01,0:28:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.53,0:28:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳不用那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.05,0:28:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本沒有人會希望發生這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.25,0:28:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我一個人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.85,0:28:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以救到多利亞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.85,0:28:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.89,0:28:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳太高估自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.53,0:28:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳以為以妳的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.21,0:28:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能改變整個國家的命運嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.85,0:28:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.13,0:28:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個國家滅亡會較好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.85,0:28:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐和伊米魯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.89,0:28:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是為這國家而煩惱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.05,0:28:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們不是傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.85,0:28:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，一個奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.57,0:28:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然說出那麼愚蠢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.81,0:28:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.89,0:29:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.85,0:29:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這兒的人都和妳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.13,0:29:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都很耽心這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望妳也明白他們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.89,0:29:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別再這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.49,0:29:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的，我明白了，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽我說，蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.85,0:29:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若然妳死了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.05,0:29:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我亦不會生存在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會陪著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.89,0:29:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀主人，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.89,0:29:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.01,0:29:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並不只屬於妳自己的，明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.89,0:29:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.49,0:29:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我這條命是屬於亞秀主人你的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.05,0:29:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.49,0:29:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都會永遠跟隨亞秀主人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.33,0:29:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有其它事情的話，屬下先告退
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.49,0:29:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.49,0:30:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.85,0:30:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若不快點完成這些資料的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.69,0:30:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.37,0:30:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.81,0:30:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.85,0:30:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼晚還未睡？有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.25,0:30:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有啊，我想你一定很辛苦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.53,0:30:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一向都不喜歡喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.13,0:30:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜妳應該很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.53,0:30:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.41,0:30:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳為何無原無故哭起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.85,0:30:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.97,0:30:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是迪歐國王派我來服侍你的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.89,0:30:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我什麼都做得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.81,0:30:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是國王…？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.17,0:30:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到我一點用處也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.05,0:30:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.49,0:30:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就喝一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.37,0:30:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實有時喝點酒也不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.49,0:30:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.25,0:30:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜，喝那麼多我一定會醉的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.89,0:31:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有我陪你睡就算醉了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.29,0:31:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.49,0:31:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我剛才說
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.85,0:31:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人你可以享用我的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.85,0:31:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.81,0:31:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯先生，莫非你討厭我？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.29,0:31:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.93,0:31:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯先生，我這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.57,0:31:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因為我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.21,0:31:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜不喜歡我呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.29,0:31:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳問我？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.97,0:31:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你對我到底怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.37,0:31:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.33,0:31:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好極了，若然這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.21,0:31:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就請伊米魯先生你收留我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.77,0:31:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一層…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.57,0:31:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯主人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.41,0:31:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你盡情享用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.05,0:32:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳說在這兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.41,0:32:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有伊米魯主人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.89,0:32:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那兒也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.93,0:32:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯主人呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.93,0:32:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.29,0:32:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜，落力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.89,0:32:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為伊米魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.01,0:32:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是妳生命中第一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.17,0:32:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.93,0:32:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.97,0:32:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你溫柔點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.57,0:32:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那這樣可以了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.09,0:32:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你做得好好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.61,0:32:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是我第一次的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.49,0:32:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.13,0:32:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但妳是迪歐國王的奴隸呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.01,0:33:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王他從來都沒享用過我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.85,0:33:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.89,0:33:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經找到一個好主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.05,0:33:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.57,0:33:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過，關於這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.85,0:33:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烏露絲已經全教過我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.17,0:33:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.53,0:33:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我都能令主人你很快樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.93,0:33:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.29,0:33:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是不是做錯了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.29,0:33:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有，妳沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.45,0:33:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳真的很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.37,0:33:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯主人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.49,0:33:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不依呀，真醜死人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.33,0:33:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，可能我是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.49,0:33:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.29,0:33:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯主人呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.01,0:34:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是沙士的商人呀，發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.89,0:34:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陣容真的很偉大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.89,0:34:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次是開評議會的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.09,0:34:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沙士的評議會終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.89,0:34:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可知多利亞的命運會怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.53,0:34:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.25,0:34:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沙士的商人已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.85,0:34:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.89,0:34:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.17,0:34:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上去通知亞秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.85,0:34:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.25,0:34:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們都是今次沙士評議會的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.85,0:34:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是來求見迪歐國王的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.89,0:34:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們有事先來函嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.49,0:34:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.37,0:34:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.49,0:34:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那請你們依照法例
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.85,0:34:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重新申請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.89,0:34:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了，沙士的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.45,0:34:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一路上長途跋涉來到多利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.93,0:34:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們做東道的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.05,0:34:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能要令各位無功而回的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:34:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.25,0:35:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位，這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.89,0:35:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請恕我唐突問一句
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.85,0:35:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為民間流傳國王遭人暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.85,0:35:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道這件事的真實性如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.85,0:35:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯確有其事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.85,0:35:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那國王他沒什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.93,0:35:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請放心，已無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.17,0:35:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位，請跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.05,0:35:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯先生，照你這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.89,0:35:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王的身體應沒大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.97,0:35:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你讓我見見大王
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.77,0:35:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到你消息那麼靈通
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.01,0:35:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.53,0:35:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是咕普達有名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.13,0:35:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑爾萬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.57,0:35:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼快就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.61,0:35:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯先生，國王在那兒呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.77,0:35:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王在大殿等候各位
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.25,0:35:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚麼，他要上殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.41,0:35:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很對不起，黑爾萬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.49,0:35:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為決定得太過倉猝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.17,0:35:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以沒時間通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.85,0:35:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實國王和沙士的商人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.25,0:35:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是那麼心急想開這評議會
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.89,0:35:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.53,0:35:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說國王…？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.57,0:35:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的，這邊請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.81,0:36:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.81,0:36:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎咕普達特派使者
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.49,0:36:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑爾萬先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.51,0:36:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.12,0:36:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王妃殿下進殿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.61,0:36:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王妃？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.89,0:36:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王到底什麼時候完婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.89,0:36:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.37,0:36:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啟稟國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.89,0:36:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們就是沙士商人的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.89,0:36:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有咕普達的黑爾萬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.77,0:36:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.37,0:36:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貴國國王遇到襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.05,0:36:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還不幸身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.33,0:36:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我代表咕普達向貴國致意
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.41,0:37:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不幸身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.85,0:37:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.89,0:37:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在不是好好的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.85,0:37:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑爾萬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.13,0:37:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想一定是你搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.05,0:37:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.17,0:37:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你似乎交待得不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.89,0:37:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然犯了那麼大的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.21,0:37:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請陛下息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.29,0:37:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經用書面正式通知各位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.45,0:37:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我以為
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.89,0:37:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位大人已經全知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.21,0:37:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.81,0:37:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,書面？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.85,0:37:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們根本沒收到任何通知
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.93,0:37:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說沒收到通知？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.77,0:37:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.05,0:37:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夠了，不用再追究原因
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.21,0:37:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你身為顧問官
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.89,0:37:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該親自去通知使者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.85,0:37:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你自己好好反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.05,0:37:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要你給我一個完滿答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.93,0:37:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑爾萬先生，真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.01,0:37:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我屬下無能，我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.93,0:37:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.29,0:37:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑爾萬先生，剛才真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.41,0:37:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在正式再向你聲明一次
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.05,0:37:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歐迪國王因為曾遇到襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.01,0:38:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然生命沒大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.85,0:38:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也再沒有那麼好精力
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.37,0:38:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去處理國家大事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.81,0:38:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以國王作出了一個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.25,0:38:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是由亞秀陛下代他處理國事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.09,0:38:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀做了國王？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.17,0:38:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.45,0:38:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.89,0:38:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀陛下的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.41,0:38:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是人所共知的前國王巴善
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.09,0:38:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.49,0:38:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯，餘下來的由我來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.17,0:38:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我向大家介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.41,0:38:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一位是我的王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.93,0:38:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亦是藍迪斯的女兒，蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.41,0:38:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這要謝亞秀陛下慧眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.93,0:38:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，基基爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.29,0:38:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒不如我和你來討論一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.77,0:38:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個沙士商人評議會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.41,0:38:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.97,0:38:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.53,0:38:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我們的議長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.45,0:38:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是謝瑞加先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.89,0:38:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.49,0:38:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.85,0:38:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你們原諒我那麼遲才到來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.25,0:38:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們所有的沙士商人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.85,0:39:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都很希望和多利亞關係
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.89,0:39:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠像現在那麼密切
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.49,0:39:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，要比現在更密切才是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.13,0:39:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們在此向陛下作出聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.05,0:39:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後多利亞的繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.57,0:39:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亦即是我們沙士商人的繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.49,0:39:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家同意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.85,0:39:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.89,0:39:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.85,0:39:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們就好好合作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.85,0:39:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這亦是我們的想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.93,0:39:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，黑爾萬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.85,0:39:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看來很煩惱似的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.85,0:39:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是有問題想問我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.85,0:39:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說得不錯，陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.89,0:39:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟你們的迪拉姆王子有關的？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.29,0:39:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為他仍然行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.45,0:39:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但這是我們兩國之間的私事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.81,0:39:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在此談我想有點不適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.93,0:39:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.37,0:39:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俗語有句話：長幼有序
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.77,0:39:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我覺得這一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該由我親自去和你們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.53,0:39:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海恩絲講清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.97,0:39:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這方法是不是較好？黑爾萬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.97,0:39:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.49,0:39:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和王妃都曾見過迪拉姆王子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.09,0:40:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我跟王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.45,0:40:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會親自和海恩絲交換意見
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.17,0:40:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定我們談過之後
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.85,0:40:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會找到迪拉姆王子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.57,0:40:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我想拜託黑爾萬先生閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.29,0:40:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幫我和王妃安排一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.05,0:40:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正式去拜訪你們國家咕普達
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會安排的了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.97,0:40:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好極了，那拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.25,0:40:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，請亞秀國王你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.05,0:40:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位使節，沒事的話就退朝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.19,0:40:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.77,0:40:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王妃殿下起駕
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.93,0:40:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶著面紗真的呼吸困難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.89,0:40:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯，不愧是貴族出身
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.97,0:40:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才妳不知幾有氣勢的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.21,0:40:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次我真的無話可說了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.29,0:41:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個都表現出色
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.85,0:41:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝主龍恩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.25,0:41:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳也很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.37,0:41:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，謝瑞加先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.53,0:41:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝瑞加先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.45,0:41:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來兩位是多利亞國
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.29,0:41:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尊貴的國王和王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.13,0:41:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們想不到，謝瑞加先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.77,0:41:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來就是沙士評議會會長
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.09,0:41:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一個很尊貴的身份呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.89,0:41:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不是你及時出現
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.89,0:41:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不知道怎去控制這種場面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.97,0:41:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們別這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.57,0:41:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們忘記了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.85,0:41:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還欠你們五十個金幣的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.81,0:41:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過，到了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.93,0:41:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉的價值升了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.85,0:41:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在已不止值五十個金幣了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.89,0:41:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自從希耶拉回來後
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.29,0:41:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該怎樣說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.21,0:41:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是遊牧民族的人經常說的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.01,0:41:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知你想說甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.45,0:41:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是好的奴隸勝過金銀財寶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.53,0:41:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.17,0:41:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯，那就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.13,0:41:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在想把希耶拉的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.85,0:41:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回復自由之身
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.17,0:41:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不再做奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.57,0:42:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自從我妻子過身
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.89,0:42:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我換過不少奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.89,0:42:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希耶拉是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.41,0:42:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.17,0:42:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想正式娶希耶拉為妻
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.85,0:42:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.37,0:42:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.41,0:42:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王甦醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.89,0:42:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？他醒過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.29,0:42:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迪歐國王你…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.05,0:42:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去找御醫來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.45,0:42:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫你去找御醫來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.85,0:42:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我想快點把體內的毒迫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.13,0:42:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.49,0:42:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.89,0:42:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊米魯，多得你想出這個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.89,0:42:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來應付這個難題
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.93,0:42:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陛下，那是我的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.85,0:42:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.13,0:42:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在我最頭痛的問題就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.37,0:42:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咕普達那邊怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.05,0:42:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.09,0:42:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨下來的問題，真令人頭痛